<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Job Offer Notification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f6f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    .email-header {
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .email-header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }
    .email-body {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #34495e;
    }
    .email-body p {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #95a5a6;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Job Offer Notification</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Dear <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>We are excited to offer you the position of <strong>{{jobTitle}}</strong> at <strong>{{companyName}}</strong>.</p>
      <p>Our HR team will reach out to you shortly to discuss the offer in more detail and guide you through the next steps, including necessary documentation and onboarding requirements.</p>
      <p>Please wait for further communication from our team. Once you confirm your acceptance, our admin will update your application status accordingly.</p>
      <p>We look forward to welcoming you to the team!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2025 {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
